						<summary>

						<p>It states that a gift of land was made by a lady named Poyyāmoḻiyāḻuḍaiyāḷ for the annual improvement of a land which she had brought under cultivation and given to the temple of Tiruchchannavaṉamuḍaiya-Nāyaṇār at Tiruttiyūr-Muṭṭam in Pāṇḍimaṇḍalam.</p>						

